i checked my myspace and ate my jacket tatie with beens and cheese, i went in the shower and washed my hair, when i got out i put my underware on and put some music on, i tied my hair up and dried my fringe, i done my makeup and put my pants on. then my mum rang me and i spoke to her, i sent louis a text saying i was going to his. i got the quarter to four bus from mine, i had to run for it.
i rang danielle when i was on the bus, then i was at the metro and had another ciggy. then i felt really sick and got a bottle of coke. i was about to get on the 44 when louis said him and james where coming into the metro, i pussyed about trying dresses on in jane norman until they got there.
when they did we saw lucy, i gave her a tab.
then we got on the 47 and went to james'
then we saw brian on his digger and he looks much better than he did last time i saw him. he's still an arsehole and a nonse though. ally has james' phone. then we saw mark, im seeing him tomorrow at bellys house.
then we went in james' and watched come dine with me whilst he ate his tea.
then we went out. it was cold.
we came back in and played monoply for two and a half hours. i came 2nd. louis lost and james won.
we had a natter then walked to the bus stop, james gave me my ipod backl.
we waited with louisn for the bus then went to my bus stop.
i got on the bus and came home.

she can have my baby when i have it.
the dog made a right fuss when i came in and i made a fuss of him. i talked to my stepdad and came on the laptop.

that was my day and i dont feel any better.

me and you are perfect for eachother.

blatently so perfect that you can walk away from me and i wont care. so perfect that you can just ditch me for other girls when we're out. so perfect for eachother that you dont have to make an effort and i wont mind.
is that what you think?
well, you're wrong. i have a brain, lik you. i have eyes, like you. i have feelings, like you. i have a heart, like you.
i dont wanna just be thrown to the side when you feel like it. just cos i love you it doesn't mean i love everything you do. and i wanna have real conversations with you. like about us. about me and about you. cos tbh, how much do we really know about eachother?
sometimes, im sitting with you and my friends and i think 'my god. how many of these has he been with?'
and it's usually the majority, this is the longest you've ever been in a ralationship. this is yourfirst relationship over two week.
when i ask you why you dont pay any attention to me anymore you tell me you love me.
i could sit here all night and swear im a boy, but you wouldn't believe me.
anyone can say anything, but to be believed you need proof.
i dont wanna loose you.
i love you, but im not a fucking idiot.

:) at south sheilds. in july. with tasha and danielle standing by, watching. i wish i could actually tell someone this. say it outloud. but, every one will be like 'it was so long ago, you two havn't spoke in weeks. forget him' well, we havn't spoke in days. no infact it's been a matter of weeks. so the next time that you need me dont expect to call. the great thing is he actually knows what he did to me. he knows how me hurt me. useeeed. cheap replacement for when camilla was in america. the first kiss was dead perfect. like, i'd always imagained a perfect couples kiss to be. we where sitting in a feild, on a sunny day. all with flowers. looken up at him, looked down. he lifted my chin up and kissed me. i pure snuggled in to him and he goes 'your perfect' and i went 'nar love, i'm not' and he goes, 'to me you are'. and it was dead lush. but when we went beach it was dead lovely. everything we done together was dead lovely. the only time i didn't wanna be near him was at that gig, 'me and camilla are back together. i love you.' he spent half the night hugging me from behind, kissing my neck, and asking me what was wrong. he spent the other half on stage talking about 'the most beautiful girl in the world' who's he'd won back that night, despite no one special trying to break them up. he made me feel like i was worth somthing when i was with him :) like i could actually do somthing in my life. like i deserved it all. 'Today was too weird. last time i woke up i was on a tropical rock, now im a thousand miles away, kissing my best friend.' i fell in love at the seaside.
